  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/5d5e82056d6bfafc5f3e95831e5cb48d.webp?t=1746436401\" width=616 height=49 /></span><br>Bass Invaders is a rhythmic fusion of classic shoot 'em up and live audio analysis.<br><br>Battle to the other side of the galaxy on a mission to save the Earth in a campaign mode with a genre-spanning soundtrack, or load <i>literally any song</i> and experience your favourite music in a new way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/6f81a52ce62d3f1bccd27e6fb2be56d1.poster.avif?t=1746436401\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/6f81a52ce62d3f1bccd27e6fb2be56d1.webm?t=1746436401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/6f81a52ce62d3f1bccd27e6fb2be56d1.mp4?t=1746436401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/c203462f701fa7909e252557dd394c04.webp?t=1746436401\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br>Play using any song you like, loading from your own files or using online video. Any track, any time. No limits.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/c630bb816af92643a556b55ac12f4eff.webp?t=1746436401\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br>High scores and ranked leaderboards for every song. Fill your ship energy levels to unleash power mode. Nail that perfect run and show your skill.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/030fa0d9a020b2464f9851fb9739ebca.webp?t=1746436401\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br>Five difficulty levels so you can just enjoy the music or really challenge your skills.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/29e5904d09b00a06fdde83513860d2c3.webp?t=1746436401\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br>Launch into a galaxy spanning campaign mode as Ace and PZO-116 battle to save the world from alien invaders. Enjoy every level with its own custom song from a genre-spanning soundtrack.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/2c59e8d0103f444292e224d24d84275d.webp?t=1746436401\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br>Two-player local co-op in every game mode (requires at least one controller). Battle through the campaign with your best friend. Play winner-stays-on with your mates and your favourite music. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/ce382427b23a259482ed910808e7533e.poster.avif?t=1746436401\" width=586 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/ce382427b23a259482ed910808e7533e.webm?t=1746436401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/ce382427b23a259482ed910808e7533e.mp4?t=1746436401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/3cd9d7d0950f857e6bb58d52dc6a5d37.webp?t=1746436401\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Custom colours<br></li><li>Colourblind modes<br></li><li>Simplified backgrounds<br></li><li>Enemy outlines<br></li><li>Gameplay assists<br></li><li>Button hints<br></li><li>Key rebinding</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/5d5e82056d6bfafc5f3e95831e5cb48d.webp?t=1746436401\" width=616 height=49 /></span><br>Bass Invaders is a rhythmic fusion of classic shoot 'em up and live audio analysis.<br><br>Battle to the other side of the galaxy on a mission to save the Earth in a campaign mode with a genre-spanning soundtrack, or load <i>literally any song</i> and experience your favourite music in a new way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/6f81a52ce62d3f1bccd27e6fb2be56d1.poster.avif?t=1746436401\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/6f81a52ce62d3f1bccd27e6fb2be56d1.webm?t=1746436401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/6f81a52ce62d3f1bccd27e6fb2be56d1.mp4?t=1746436401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/c203462f701fa7909e252557dd394c04.webp?t=1746436401\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br>Play using any song you like, loading from your own files or using online video. Any track, any time. No limits.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738680/extras/c630bb816af92643a556b55ac12f4eff.webp?t=1746436401\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br>High scores and ranked leaderboards for every song. Fill your ship energy levels to unleash power mode. Nail that perfect run and show your skill.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_